dct_title_s: London and Westminster in the reign of Queen Elizabeth, anno Dom., 1563
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Bird's-eye-view. William Darton was located at 58 Holborn Hill after 1810; cf. Tooley's dictionary of mapmakers. Includes text, index to points of interest, and illus. of notable buildings.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Published by William Darton, 58 Holborn Hill, [after 1810]
